---
const metrics = [
  {
    label: "Tiempo de Actividad",
    value: "99.9%",
    stat: "Revenue",
    change: "+0.1%",
    changeType: "positive"
  },
  {
    label: "Velocidad de Datos",
    value: "1.2 Gbps",
    stat: "Growth",
    change: "+15%",
    changeType: "positive"
  },
  {
    label: "Conexiones Activas",
    value: "1.5M",
    stat: "Active Users",
    change: "+8.3%",
    changeType: "positive"
  },
  {
    label: "Satisfacción del Cliente",
    value: "98%",
    change: "+2.1%",
    changeType: "positive"
  }
];
---

<section class="hero light-hero">
  <div class="container hero-container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Innovando en Telecomunicaciones con Vortex</h1>
      <p>
        En Vortex Telecommunications, ofrecemos soluciones de vanguardia para conectar al mundo. 
        Desde internet de alta velocidad hasta servicios en la nube seguros, empoderamos a empresas 
        y personas para prosperar en la era digital.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <button class="btn btn-primary">Empezar</button>
        <button class="btn btn-secondary">Saber más</button>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-logos">
        <img src="./logo1.svg" alt="Logo" class="logo-item" />
        <img src="./logo2.svg" alt="Logo" class="logo-item" />
        <img src="./logo3.svg" alt="Logo" class="logo-item" />
        <img src="./logo4.svg" alt="Logo" class="logo-item" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-dashboard">
      <div class="dashboard-stats">
        <div class="stats-header">
          <h3>Performance</h3>
          <div class="period-selector">
            <span class="active">1S</span>
            <span>1M</span>
            <span>3M</span>
            <span>1A</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stats-chart">
          <canvas id="performanceChart"></canvas>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dashboard-metrics">
        {metrics.map((metric) => (
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="label">{metric.label}</span>
            <span class="value" data-stat={metric.stat}>{metric.value}</span>
            <span class={`change ${metric.changeType}`}>{metric.change}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>